mxklabs.expr

* Remove types that don't add anything: BitvectorExprDef and others.
* Implement cone-of-influence filter for index-like operators as some ops may not matter 
  and don't need to be converted.
* Check attrs before ops/sub_valtypes.
* Add 'logical' or 'prop' expr_def_set.

  ctx.prop.logical_and(...)

* Add support for bitvectors.
* Add support for dictionaries mapping strings of types.

  ctx.valtypes.bitvector(width=10)
  ctx.bitvector.bitwise_and(bitv1, bitv2)

  ctx.expr.bitvector_add()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_subtr()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_mult()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_div()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_mod()

  ctx.expr.bitvector_gt()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_gte()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_lt()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_lte()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_eq()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_ne()

  ctx.expr.bitvector_tobool()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_frombool()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_slice()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_concat()
  ctx.expr.bitvector_index()

* Add bitvector expr_def_set.
* Add index operators for vector, a shorthand for operator[] on Expr to generate it.
* Add index operators for dictionary, a shorthand for operator[] on Expr to generate it.

* Add support for heterogeneous tuples of types.
* Add support for homogeneous, fixed-size vectors of types.

* Better error messages (file + line numbers)
